Biologically Inspired Multi-scale keyPoints 
-------------------------------------------

For more details, see

Kasim TerziÄ‡, J.M.F. Rodrigues and J.M.H. du Buf: 
Fast Cortical Keypoints for Real-Time Object Recognition, 
Proc. ICIP 2013, Melbourne, Sep 2013

J.M.F. Rodrigues and J.M.H. du Buf:
A cortical framework for invariant object categorization and recognition,
Cognitive Processing, Vol. 10, No. 3, pp. 243-261, 2009

