Requirements
------------
CMake 2.8+
OpenCV 2.3+
C++ compiler
OpenMP (recommended)
Doxygen (optional)

Tested with 
-----------
GCC 4.7, 4.8
OpenCV 2.3.0, 2.4.2
Debian 6, 7
Ubuntu 12.04
Windows 7 (with MinGW)

Building instructions
---------------------

Unix/Linux:

mkdir build
cd build
cmake ..
make
make doc

Windows/Mac:

Use CMake GUI to create a project for your preferred IDE.

Documentation
-------------
Documentation will be generated by Doxygen and stored in the "doc" folder.

Getting started
---------------
A minimal usage example is found in testkps.cpp


Kasim Terzic, Jun 2013
kterzic@ualg.pt
